,327,71,345],"class_list":["post-37552","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-sin-al-ithm","tag-ablution-wudu","tag-call-to-prayer-adhan","tag-congregational-prayer-salat-jamaah","tag-excellence-al-ihsan","tag-expiation-al-kaffarah","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-guidance-al-hidayah","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-hypocrisy-al-nifaq","tag-misguidance-dallaal","tag-mosques-masjid","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-records","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-sickness-al-marad","tag-sunnah","tag-warning-al-nudhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9LG","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":5237,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/16\/dua-taqwa-huda-afaf-ghani\/","url_meta":{"origin":37552,"position":0},"title":"Hadith of Dua: The Prophet asks for guidance, independence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I ask You for guidance, righteousness, abstinence, and independence.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2721 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0651 \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0650\u0651\u064a \u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0644\u064f\u0643\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/tashahhud-fi-hajjah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37552,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Testifying to faith in prayer and in need","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, taught us to bear witness to faith in prayer and to bear witness to faith in times of need. Bearing witness in prayer is to say, \u201cGreetings are for Allah, as are prayers and pure things.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15065,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/15\/prophet-hurry-break-fast\/","url_meta":{"origin":37552,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: The Prophet hastens to break his fast","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu 'Atiyyah reported: Masruq and I visited Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, and he said, \u201cO mother of the believers, there are two companions of Muhammad and neither of them hold back from doing good. One of them hastens to break his fast and to perform the evening\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":